Informations de dépendance

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>sudoku</groupId>
  <artifactId>sudo</artifactId>
  <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'sudoku:sudo:jar:1.0-SNAPSHOT'

Apache Ivy

<dependency org="sudoku" name="sudo" rev="1.0-SNAPSHOT">
  <artifact name="sudo" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='sudoku', module='sudo', version='1.0-SNAPSHOT')
)

Gradle/Grails

compile 'sudoku:sudo:1.0-SNAPSHOT'

Scala SBT

libraryDependencies += "sudoku" % "sudo" % "1.0-SNAPSHOT"

Leiningen
